comments.text: Great post Jon!  Like I had mentioned previously I saw him at The Boston Garden in 1974. I was a senior in Highschool. Sadly I really don't remember to much about the show.  I do recall the beginning of Funeral for a Friend ,the smoke, and the lighting of the neon ELTON JOHN when Loves Lie Bleeding s piano ramps up . And Saturday Nights Alright for Fighting seemed to go on forever. And I wasn't drinking or Smoking LoL
